summary: Little video of overworked office workers ranting about their bosses. Sorry for the repost, I forgot to mention that the texture...
caption:
Little video of overworked office workers ranting about their bosses.

Sorry for the repost, I forgot to mention that the texture I used comes from 神崎柚 (pixiv id=745675).

This will be my last illustration for 2018. When I started drawing, exactly one year ago, I would have never imagined receiving such an amount of support. Thank you so much for encouraging me throughout this journey.

I wish you happy holidays, and I hope to see you soon.

summary:
Aggressive Retsuko
Aggretsuko
Rating: 3/3
Categories: animal protagonist, comedy, dub, music, original work, sanrio, slice of...
body:
Aggressive Retsuko

Aggretsuko

Rating: 3/3

Categories: animal protagonist, comedy, dub, music, original work, sanrio, slice of life, work life

Red panda office worker who goes to karaoke bars to sing death metal about the annoyances of everyday life. Relatable asf. The first season may seem daunting but each episode is only a minute long so it won’t even take two hours to complete.

S1, 100 eps (sub only)

ONA, 10 eps

We Wish You a Metal Christmas, 1 ep

ONA S2, 10 eps
